LogFile.FinalText: Incredible how much they look alike. That is what many people think of the princesses of Denmark. There are many similarities between Mary and Marie but just as many - if not more differences. They are both from abroad, not royalities and have both found their prince of Denmark - Mary is married to Crown Prince of Denmark Frederik and Marie with prince Joachim. Their names and looks are exceptionally alike. Both are extraordinary beautiful with long dark hair and big brown eyes. But in spite of the many similarities, Mary and Marie are also two individuals who have had and have very different lives which have influenced their values and characters.
